

selector {
    property: value; //color, front-size, background, border 
    property: value;
    property: value;
    property: value;
}

//universal selector
* { }

//element selector
p { } img { } h1 { } table { }

//class selector
.home-section { }

//id selector 
#home { }

//attribute selector
a[href="https://google.com"] {
    property: value;
}

// group selectors
p, h1, h2, h3 { }

// pseudo-class selector
a :hover { }
input :focus { }


PRIORITY

1. inline style
2. id seclector 
3. class selector, attribute, pseudo-class
4. element selector 
5. universal selector 
